properties.property: This is the final battle. Our cleanup operation can only begin once the infection has been subdued. This is the main infection site, it must be quarantined. Mission objectives: -Select a faction. -Protect the Ether Anchors. -Eliminate all threats.
Orbital bombardment has driven most of the infection underground. If we can secure the area, the ether anchors will give us the power needed to halt the spread.

The last Krovnork threat has been eliminated.
The remnants will succumb to the infection and die. The Ether Anchors are no longer endangered by them.

Dardarndroe activity is subsiding, this area is ours.
The Ether Anchors will quantum-lock the planet to counteract the spread of infection. Our cleanup operation will now begin.
It will take time, but this planet has been saved.
Good work, everyone.

A huge mass of corrupted matter has emerged.
The hive must be frightened by our advance.
We cannot let them hold the Ether Anchors!
